## 🔧 Technical Implementation Notes

### CSS Requirements:
```css
/* Fixed container approach */
.hero-container {
  width: 1280px;
  height: 831px;
  position: relative;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: #fffcf9;
}

/* Scale for smaller viewports */
@media (max-width: 1280px) {
  .hero-container {
    transform: scale(calc(100vw / 1280));
    transform-origin: top center;
  }
}

/* DM Sans optical sizing */
.dm-sans-text {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 14;
}
```

### Component Structure:
```
HeroSection
├── BackgroundTitle (z-index: 0)
├── LeftContentColumn (z-index: 10)
│   ├── OriginTag
│   ├── Description
│   └── CTAButton
├── GroundShadow (z-index: 3)
├── ChairImage (z-index: 5)
├── FloorLamp (z-index: 4)
├── ThumbnailStrip (z-index: 20)
│   ├── ArrowBadge
│   └── ThumbnailCards × 3
└── BottomBar (z-index: 30)
    ├── DarkBar
    ├── CircleButton
    └── DecorativeCutouts
```

