## 🎯 Success Criteria

- [ ] All elements positioned within 2px of Figma specifications at 1280px
- [ ] Typography matches exactly (font, size, weight, optical settings)
- [ ] Colors match hex values precisely
- [ ] Z-index layering creates proper depth
- [ ] Image crops and transforms match original
- [ ] Button states and interactions work smoothly
- [ ] Responsive scaling maintains proportions
- [ ] Mobile layout provides usable alternative while preserving brand

---

## 📱 Responsive Considerations

### Desktop (1280px+):
- Use exact Figma specifications
- All elements visible
- Fixed layout

### Tablet (768px - 1279px):
- Proportionally scale entire layout
- Consider stacking thumbnails horizontally below hero
- Maintain spatial relationships

### Mobile (< 768px):
- Redesign with vertical flow
- Stack content: Title → Chair → Text → CTA → Thumbnails
- Simplify bottom navigation
- Ensure touch targets are 44px minimum

